OL,3,CAirport security rules explained as
OL,4,Cplans to scrap 100ml liquid rule
OL,5,Creversed
OL,7,FPassengers travelling to Bristol
OL,8,FAirport are being warned to be aware
OL,9,Fof the new rules at security following
OL,10,Fa number of changes.
OL,12,FThose travelling through the airport
OL,13,Fwere told they would no longer need to
OL,14,Fremove liquids, laptops and
OL,15,Felectronics from their hand luggage
OL,16,Fwhen passing through security last
OL,17,Fmonth.
