OL,3,CAirport security rules explained as
OL,4,Cplans to scrap 100ml liquid rule
OL,5,Creversed
OL,7,FOther changes includes people now
OL,8,Femptying the contents of their pockets
OL,9,Finto their bag, rather than into a
OL,10,Ftray, before going through a scanner,
OL,11,Fand emptying the contents of metal
OL,12,Fwater bottles.
OL,14,FThe airport also added that the long-
OL,15,Fheld rule of only being able to bring
OL,16,Fcontainers of liquids up to 100ml was
OL,17,Fbeing scrapped - and that passengers
OL,18,Fcould now carry bottles, sprays or
OL,19,Fcreams of up to 330ml.
