OL,3,CAirport security rules explained as
OL,4,Cplans to scrap 100ml liquid rule
OL,5,Creversed
OL,7,FThe change in policy was announced
OL,8,Fafter the airport invested #11.5m on
OL,9,Fnew scanners, and was due to come into
OL,10,Feffect at Bristol Airport on 14 June.
OL,12,FBut the Government has now reversed a
OL,13,Fkey part of these plans, meaning the
OL,14,F100ml rule on liquids will remain in
OL,15,Fplace for the time being.
