OL,3,CAirport security rules explained as
OL,4,Cplans to scrap 100ml liquid rule
OL,5,Creversed
OL,7,FThe Government had required that all
OL,8,Fairports install the new scanners
OL,9,Fequipped to allow liquids of up to two
OL,10,Flitres in volume to be stored in hand
OL,11,Fluggage when passengers go through
OL,12,Fsecurity.
OL,14,FBut larger UK airports including
OL,15,FHeathrow, Gatwick and Manchester
OL,16,Freportedly missed the deadline of 1
OL,17,FJune due to logistical issues.
