OL,3,CAirport security rules explained as
OL,4,Cplans to scrap 100ml liquid rule
OL,5,Creversed
OL,7,FThis led the Department for Transport
OL,8,F(DfT) to unexpectedly announce that
OL,9,Ffrom June 9 the old rule ` only
OL,10,Fallowing liquids, gels and pastes
OL,11,Funder 100ml to be taken through
OL,12,Fsecurity ` would be reinstated.
OL,14,FThe DfT said: "This temporary move is
OL,15,Fto enable further improvements to be
OL,16,Fmade to the new checkpoint systems and
OL,17,Fwill only affect a small number of
OL,18,Fpassengers."
