OL,3,CAirport security rules explained as
OL,4,Cplans to scrap 100ml liquid rule
OL,5,Creversed
OL,7,FBut the late change has led to
OL,8,Fcriticism from the Airport Operators
OL,9,FAssociation.
OL,11,FKaren Dee, the chief executive, said:
OL,12,F"These latest changes announced on
OL,13,FFriday 7 June, instigated with very
OL,14,Flittle notice, have created
OL,15,Funcertainty for passengers just as
OL,16,Fairports enter their busiest periods
OL,17,Fof the year.
