OL,3,CAirport security rules explained as
OL,4,Cplans to scrap 100ml liquid rule
OL,5,Creversed
OL,7,F"It has also put airport operators in
OL,8,Fa challenging position, with very
OL,9,Flimited time to prepare for the
OL,10,Fadditional staffing and wider
OL,11,Fresources that this will require, and
OL,12,Fno clear idea of when this issue will
OL,13,Fbe resolved."
OL,15,FIn response, the DfT added: "It only
OL,16,Faffects those travelling from six
OL,17,Fregional airports where next
OL,18,Fgeneration security checkpoints (NGSC)
OL,19,Fwere already in full operation `
OL,20,Faround 6% of all UK air passengers.
